{"tid":1617393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔宣言〕10月4日中環蒙面遊行宣言","createTime":"2019-10-03T18:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T03:21:45.000Z","uid":267052,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"67738c3b49863f3cb548e62ae108410f74d7eada","tid":1617393,"uid":267052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:41:41.000Z","msg":"有聞林鄭政府將引《緊急法》推行《禁蒙面法》，我等一眾香港市民強烈反對。今日集結，我等在此對政權宣佈：<br />\n<br />\n一，政府強推禁蒙面法，無視社會亂局根因。<br />\n禁蒙面法推動組以止暴制亂為名，強推法案，不經宣傳，未有諮詢。此舉實是高官漠視民意，欲掩己過的證明：我城之「暴」，非示威者以肉身撼強權，乃警員當胸實彈射擊學生，事後無恥粉飾行為之暴；我城之亂，非因示威者以言伐制度，乃因特首一意孤行，不肯答允民間五大訴求所致。粗暴、倉促地通過禁蒙面法，只能反映官員諉過抗爭者，而不願反思己身的滔天大錯，以為強硬鎮壓示威，便可讓香港如常的不切實際。<br />\n<br />\n二，面對強權打壓，我等毫無懼意。<br />\n禁蒙面法，無非是林鄭政府妄想令人生畏，停止抗爭的手段。高高在上的官員認為，蒙面讓抗爭者任意妄為，卻不知早喪盡良心的正是自己；以為禁蒙面可讓抗爭者擔驚受怕，從此不敢發聲，免被秋後算賬，殊不知抗爭者模糊面目，除是避免政權清算，亦是為了融入諸眾如水，使團結的香港市民可砥礪前行如堅冰。今日我等蒙面，非為掩蓋面容，而為合眾為一。口罩、豬嘴、面具之下，只存對準政權及其執法機器的悲憤，永無恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民非以蒙面武裝自己不可，歸根究底，是誰之過？反修例風波遲遲未息，乃誰之錯？我等勸喻林鄭政府反省自身，勿用無止境的強硬條例，將我城推向深淵。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"e80c3c43f1c3edce853bdc442b199885f68c37df","tid":1617393,"uid":30563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:42:41.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3247659243702490e014d15a4699e0665106e2fb","tid":1617393,"uid":267052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:46:52.000Z","msg":"因為好似見唔到有宣言 所以寫咗<br />\n應該可以再改 方便人讀可能會好啲<br />\n我知我p牌 自己先摺埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8f68915667ed49603037f33bcb0e988db80533","tid":1617393,"uid":267052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:50:16.000Z","msg":"係咪可以自己pish自己<br />\n噉我試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"51652bf7119fc70abe7f774ff19abba765ee5b0b","tid":1617393,"uid":267052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:50:29.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"b9dfe90f74d76479cbdd537c3aa32256ace61ee7","tid":1617393,"uid":267052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:51:09.000Z","msg":"畢竟比較想聽日有宣言 所以<br />\n3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b380aa57c6e18598616c26718db676eae93792","tid":1617393,"uid":267052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:52:38.000Z","msg":"We are not background ar!<br />\n數到幾話&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n哦4/10"},{"pid":"933cb15162e785d5bb518a9649bce2fe7a0b8604","tid":1617393,"uid":267052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:55:20.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"d3d238bc1303c9fce9b7cd4e3c8a14880f9923b6","tid":1617393,"uid":267052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:45:36.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"b1b5c588f2dcbdc8b43a1986fee1992e255eaa6b","tid":1617393,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bddc2e415ca05cd4db39db93e4cc1eae678b02d","tid":1617393,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a546c81297b2e21df5c6e70d2639a2ce8044fc","tid":1617393,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:47:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fd292c32db9b1b7faa2552215636114784ed0c8","tid":1617393,"uid":100420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:59:56.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f8186d2f7bf77070734b51fd4021327964ba152c","tid":1617393,"uid":136233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:15:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8b83d2fe311342f76e8444d14a1e0da939c5334","tid":1617393,"uid":284529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:16:39.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到<br />\n<br />\n全力支持!!"},{"pid":"45beab72600a12f76d2be682f0f0605793e49ca2","tid":1617393,"uid":187489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:41:36.000Z","msg":"派口罩/口號叫：香港人 戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非：</span><br />\n喺街見到人借locker要帶<span style=\"color: pink;\">鎖</span><br />\n有人口渴要帶<span style=\"color: pink;\">罐裝飲品</span><br />\n病左最起碼要<span style=\"color: pink;\">戴口罩</span><br />\n喺示威地區附近行街要<span style=\"color: pink;\">戴豬嘴</span><br />\n樣衰要<span style=\"color: pink;\">遮樣/遮耳</span><br />\n顯瘦要<span style=\"color: red;\">全黑</span><br />\n潮人着衫要fast fashion：<span style=\"color: pink;\">越平越好</span>，有螢光粉都<span style=\"color: pink;\">可以即棄</span>，Apple Watch 買平錶帶，換過條都唔肉赤<br />\n想靚靚就要着純色<span style=\"color: pink;\">冇brand、冇logo、唔好戴accessories</span><br />\n秋風起，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">着風褸笠住個頭防色防粉防水防露髮型耳仔</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ba3fab8aa1b87480a028dc170e8a401691fc2e","tid":1617393,"uid":157550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:45:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba1f3edb10265d1cfb47c97f1a858ec4b5d234ea","tid":1617393,"uid":119181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:49:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da2a74f31c4a9058f0206ccaf5228ce864bdf8ca","tid":1617393,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb051e20c58bccabe9508e900cbfb80fc973ea5","tid":1617393,"uid":157550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:01:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d24870c36283b52e290afb273a2452599461569","tid":1617393,"uid":283650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:07:50.000Z","msg":"推啊！"},{"pid":"97a550cc16f2b4e4d5b676f543e2d78de08c4be5","tid":1617393,"uid":189077